                    <li>Most powerful and highest battery-capacity vehicle on this list under ₹15 L</li>
                    <li>Spacious, modern interior, with robust feature set</li>
                </ul>

                <h5 class="">Considerations</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li>Highest running costs if battery rented; upfront price teeters at ₹14 L</li>
                    <li>MG's charging network is improving but still lags Tata</li>
